# Agents — Frontend (AI Elements)

All chat UI primitives come from `src/components/ai-elements/` — components copied from [elements.ai-sdk.dev](https://elements.ai-sdk.dev).
**Always check the docs before writing any custom chat UI.**

If you need a complete usage example, ask the user to share `src/components/ChatView.tsx`.

