## Backend Integration

The backend exposes an OpenAI-compatible `/api/v1/agents/chat/completions` endpoint.
Connect via `useChat` from `@ai-sdk/react` with `DefaultChatTransport`:

```tsx
import { useChat } from "@ai-sdk/react";
import { DefaultChatTransport } from "ai";

const transport = useMemo(
  () =>
    new DefaultChatTransport({
      api: "/api/v1/agents/chat/completions",
      body: () => ({ model: agentIdRef.current, stream: true, user: userId, session_id: sessionId }),
    }),
  [userId, sessionId],
);

const { messages, sendMessage, status, stop } = useChat({ id: sessionId, transport });
```

Streaming delivers `UIMessage.parts[]` with types `"reasoning"` and `"text"`. Always sort reasoning before text when rendering.
